{
  "verses": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "verse_number": 1,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:1",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَمَّ يَتَسَآءَلُونَ",
      "translation": "Tentang apakah mereka saling bertanya-tanya?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "verse_number": 2,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:2",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "عَنِ ٱلنَّبَإِ ٱلۡعَظِيمِ",
      "translation": "Tentang berita yang besar (hari berbangkit),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "verse_number": 3,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:3",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ٱلَّذِي هُمۡ فِيهِ مُخۡتَلِفُونَ",
      "translation": "yang dalam hal itu mereka berselisih.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "verse_number": 4,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:4",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ",
      "translation": "Tidak!892) Kelak mereka akan mengetahui,",
      "footnotes": "*892) Sanggahan terhadap pendapat orang-orang kafir Mekkah yang mengingkari hari berbangkit dan hari Kiamat."
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "verse_number": 5,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:5",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَيَعۡلَمُونَ",
      "translation": "sekali lagi tidak! Kelak mereka akan mengetahui.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "verse_number": 6,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:6",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "أَلَمۡ نَجۡعَلِ ٱلۡأَرۡضَ مِهَٰدٗا",
      "translation": "Bukankah Kami telah menjadikan bumi sebagai hamparan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "verse_number": 7,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:7",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَٱلۡجِبَالَ أَوۡتَادٗا",
      "translation": "dan gunung-gunung sebagai pasak?",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "verse_number": 8,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:8",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَخَلَقۡنَٰكُمۡ أَزۡوَٰجٗا",
      "translation": "Dan Kami menciptakan kamu berpasang-pasangan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "verse_number": 9,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:9",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَعَلۡنَا نَوۡمَكُمۡ سُبَاتٗا",
      "translation": "dan Kami menjadikan tidurmu untuk istirahat,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "verse_number": 10,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:10",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلَّيۡلَ لِبَاسٗا",
      "translation": "dan Kami menjadikan malam sebagai pakaian,893)",
      "footnotes": "*893) Malam itu disebut sebagai \"pakaian\" karena malam itu gelap menutupi jagat sebagaimana pakaian menutupi tubuh manusia."
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "verse_number": 11,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:11",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَعَلۡنَا ٱلنَّهَارَ مَعَاشٗا",
      "translation": "dan Kami menjadikan siang untuk mencari penghidupan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "verse_number": 12,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:12",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَبَنَيۡنَا فَوۡقَكُمۡ سَبۡعٗا شِدَادٗا",
      "translation": "dan Kami membangun di atas kamu tujuh (lapis langit) yang kokoh,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "verse_number": 13,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:13",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَعَلۡنَا سِرَاجٗا وَهَّاجٗا",
      "translation": "dan Kami menjadikan pelita yang terang-benderang (matahari),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "verse_number": 14,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:14",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَأَنزَلۡنَا مِنَ ٱلۡمُعۡصِرَٰتِ مَآءٗ ثَجَّاجٗا",
      "translation": "dan Kami turunkan dari awan, air hujan yang tercurah dengan lebatnya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "verse_number": 15,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:15",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّنُخۡرِجَ بِهِۦ حَبّٗا وَنَبَاتٗا",
      "translation": "untuk Kami tumbuhkan dengan air itu biji-bijian dan tanam-tanaman,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "verse_number": 16,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:16",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَجَنَّٰتٍ أَلۡفَافًا",
      "translation": "dan kebun-kebun yang rindang.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "verse_number": 17,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:17",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ يَوۡمَ ٱلۡفَصۡلِ كَانَ مِيقَٰتٗا",
      "translation": "Sungguh, hari keputusan adalah suatu waktu yang telah ditetapkan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "verse_number": 18,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:18",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ يُنفَخُ فِي ٱلصُّورِ فَتَأۡتُونَ أَفۡوَاجٗا",
      "translation": "(yaitu) pada hari (ketika) sangkakala ditiup, lalu kamu datang berbondong-bondong,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "verse_number": 19,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:19",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَفُتِحَتِ ٱلسَّمَآءُ فَكَانَتۡ أَبۡوَٰبٗا",
      "translation": "dan langit pun dibukalah, maka terdapatlah beberapa pintu,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "verse_number": 20,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:20",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَسُيِّرَتِ ٱلۡجِبَالُ فَكَانَتۡ سَرَابًا",
      "translation": "dan gunung-gunungpun dijalankan sehingga menjadi fatamorgana.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "verse_number": 21,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:21",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ جَهَنَّمَ كَانَتۡ مِرۡصَادٗا",
      "translation": "Sungguh, (neraka) Jahanam itu (sebagai) tempat mengintai (bagi penjaga yang mengawasi isi neraka),",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "verse_number": 22,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:22",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لِّلطَّٰغِينَ مَـَٔابٗا",
      "translation": "menjadi tempat kembali bagi orang-orang yang melampaui batas.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "verse_number": 23,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:23",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّٰبِثِينَ فِيهَآ أَحۡقَابٗا",
      "translation": "Mereka tinggal di sana dalam masa yang lama,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "verse_number": 24,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:24",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّا يَذُوقُونَ فِيهَا بَرۡدٗا وَلَا شَرَابًا",
      "translation": "mereka tidak merasakan kesejukan di dalamnya dan tidak (pula mendapat) minuman,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "verse_number": 25,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:25",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِلَّا حَمِيمٗا وَغَسَّاقٗا",
      "translation": "selain air yang mendidih dan nanah,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "verse_number": 26,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:26",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "جَزَآءٗ وِفَاقًا",
      "translation": "sebagai pembalasan yang setimpal.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "verse_number": 27,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:27",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّهُمۡ كَانُواْ لَا يَرۡجُونَ حِسَابٗا",
      "translation": "Sesungguhnya dahulu mereka tidak pernah mengharapkan perhitungan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "verse_number": 28,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:28",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَكَذَّبُواْ بِـَٔايَٰتِنَا كِذَّابٗا",
      "translation": "dan mereka benar-benar mendustakan ayat-ayat Kami.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "verse_number": 29,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:29",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَكُلَّ شَيۡءٍ أَحۡصَيۡنَٰهُ كِتَٰبٗا",
      "translation": "Dan segala sesuatu telah Kami catat dalam suatu Kitab (buku catatan amalan manusia).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "verse_number": 30,
      "page_number": 582,
      "verse_key": "78:30",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "فَذُوقُواْ فَلَن نَّزِيدَكُمۡ إِلَّا عَذَابًا",
      "translation": "Maka karena itu rasakanlah! Maka tidak ada yang akan Kami tambahkan kepadamu selain azab.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "verse_number": 31,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:31",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "إِنَّ لِلۡمُتَّقِينَ مَفَازًا",
      "translation": "Sungguh, orang-orang yang bertakwa mendapat kemenangan,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "verse_number": 32,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:32",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "حَدَآئِقَ وَأَعۡنَٰبٗا",
      "translation": "(yaitu) kebun-kebun dan buah anggur,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "verse_number": 33,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:33",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَكَوَاعِبَ أَتۡرَابٗا",
      "translation": "dan gadis-gadis belia yang sebaya,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "verse_number": 34,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:34",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "وَكَأۡسٗا دِهَاقٗا",
      "translation": "dan gelas-gelas yang penuh (berisi minuman).",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "verse_number": 35,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:35",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "لَّا يَسۡمَعُونَ فِيهَا لَغۡوٗا وَلَا كِذَّٰبٗا",
      "translation": "Di sana mereka tidak mendengar percakapan yang sia-sia maupun (perkataan) dusta.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "verse_number": 36,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:36",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "جَزَآءٗ مِّن رَّبِّكَ عَطَآءً حِسَابٗا",
      "translation": "Sebagai balasan dan pemberian yang cukup banyak dari Tuhanmu,",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 37,
      "verse_number": 37,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:37",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "رَّبِّ ٱلسَّمَٰوَٰتِ وَٱلۡأَرۡضِ وَمَا بَيۡنَهُمَا ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنِۖ لَا يَمۡلِكُونَ مِنۡهُ خِطَابٗا",
      "translation": "Tuhan (yang memelihara) langit dan bumi serta apa yang ada di antara keduanya; Yang Maha Pengasih, mereka tidak mampu berbicara dengan Dia.",
      "footnotes": ""
    },
    {
      "id": 38,
      "verse_number": 38,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:38",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "يَوۡمَ يَقُومُ ٱلرُّوحُ وَٱلۡمَلَٰٓئِكَةُ صَفّٗاۖ لَّا يَتَكَلَّمُونَ إِلَّا مَنۡ أَذِنَ لَهُ ٱلرَّحۡمَٰنُ وَقَالَ صَوَابٗا",
      "translation": "Pada hari, ketika rūḥ894) dan para malaikat berdiri bersaf-saf, mereka tidak berkata-kata, kecuali siapa yang telah diberi izin kepadanya oleh Tuhan Yang Maha Pengasih dan dia hanya mengatakan yang benar.",
      "footnotes": "*894) Para mufasir mempunyai pendapat yang berbeda tentang maksud \"rūḥ\" dalam ayat ini. Ada yang mengatakan \"Jibril\" ada yang mengatakan \"tentara Allah\" dan ada pula yang mengatakan \"roh manusia.\""
    },
    {
      "id": 39,
      "verse_number": 39,
      "page_number": 583,
      "verse_key": "78:39",
      "juz_number": 30,
      "hizb_number": 59,
      "rub_el_hizb_number": 233,
      "sajdah_type": null,
      "sajdah_number": null,
      "text": "ذَٰلِكَ ٱلۡيَوۡمُ ٱلۡحَقُّۖ فَمَن شَآءَ ٱتَّخَذَ إِلَىٰ رَبِّهِۦ مَـَٔابًا",
      "translation": "Itulah hari yang pasti terjadi. Maka barangsiapa menghendaki, niscaya dia menempuh jalan kembali kepada Tuhannya.",
      "footnotes": ""
